<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-44-0254 </DOCNO><TEXT>A case study is presented which illustrates the role of a modern energyconsultancy company in achieving energy savings for an industrial company.TM Energy carried out a free scoping study to assess the opportunitiesfor energy cost reduction at Automative Products, U.K. Total savingsof Pound 857,000 p.a. were identified for a total projected capital expenditureof Pound 1.91M with a significant proportion available for little orno capital cost. Some useful pointers to assist companies obtain valuefor money when choosing energy consultant companies are given. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>